snippet.title: Countryhumans Dating Sim - Official Game Trailer
snippet.description:
You're going to a new school (✰•* wow *•✰) . You're greeted by 3 twi- Twinkies and they show you around school. You can confess to one of the 4 main or six 6 side characters.
--
Links:
 The game - https://johns-emazing-films.itch.io/countryhumans-dating-sim
 Discord server - https://discord.com/invite/XsrkP3W
 Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/johns.emazing.films/
 Twitter - https://twitter.com/johnsemazing
--
Music used - ''Take me'' by Casiopea - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZNL1qYk06mE

--
Features:
 13 endings (as of now)
 A lot of locations (a of now)
 Inventory system and items you can give to characters
 In-game phone with character info
--
Things added in 0.12:
 Mexico, Philippines, and more.
 3 new routes
 Stats
 and some other stuff
--
Thanks for reading the description
